# Allowlist hosts file for DNS filtering
# Format: <proxy_ip> <hostname>
# 
# These hostnames resolve to their respective proxy container IPs
# The proxy containers handle the actual connection to the internet

# GitHub (code hosting, git operations)
10.100.1.10 github.com
10.100.1.10 www.github.com

# GitHub API (for GitHub App tokens and MCP server)
10.100.1.15 api.github.com

# GitHub raw content (for fetching raw files)
10.100.1.11 raw.githubusercontent.com

# GitHub codeload (for downloading archives/zips)
10.100.1.12 codeload.github.com

# Godot documentation
10.100.1.13 docs.godotengine.org

# Anthropic API (for Claude Code)
10.100.1.14 api.anthropic.com

# Note: These IPs are static assignments within the sandbox_net
# They must match the ipv4_address settings in compose.base.yml
# Also: Domains must be listed in the Corefile server block
